Package: glm.deploy
Type: Package
Title: Generates the source code of the scoring algorithm (predict) of a GLM object to C or JAVA to deploy/operationalize it outside R.
Version: 1.0.0
Author@s: c(person("Oscar","Castro-Lopez",email="oscarcastro@uas.edu.mx", role=c("aut","cre")), person("Ines", "Vega-Lopez"), role=c("aut","cre"))
Author: Oscar Castro-Lopez, Ines Vega-Lopez
Maintainer: Oscar J. Castro-LÃ³pez <oscarcastro@uas.edu.mx>
License: GPL (>= 2.1)
Description: The glm.deploy models allows to generate the specific scoring algorithm (predict) of a trained model in C or JAVA source code. Allowing to deploy/operationalize gerealized linear models (glm) outside R. It generates two functions: 1) the equivalent to predict(type="response") and 2) the equivalent to predict(type="link").
